# Third-party submissions — keep the directory and its README but ignore
# everyone else's agent code by default. Our own reference baselines are
# explicit exceptions so they ship with the bench.
submissions/*
!submissions/README.md
!submissions/python-baseline/
!submissions/python-baseline/**
